summary: You can now wear the Executioner Armor
descriptionHtml:
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~WEARABLE EXEUTIONER ARMOR~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~BY: ALFATOSSA~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~


INSTALLATION:

-Put the \\\"Wearable_Executioner Armor.esp\\\" file in your \\\"C:\\\\Program Files (x86)\\\\SteamApps\\\\common\\\\skyrim\\\\data\\\" folder
-Activate it in the data file tab on the Skyrim launcher
-Enjoy!


DESCRIPTION:

It allows you to wear the Exeutioner Armor complete set.
author: Alfatossa
